title: Karl-Erik Svensson
text:
Karl-Erik Svensson (February 20, 1891 - November 9, 1978) was a <a href="Sweden">Swedish</a> <a href="gymnast">gymnast</a> who competed in the <a href="1912%20Summer%20Olympics">1912 Summer Olympics</a>.
He was part of the Swedish team, which won the gold medal in the gymnastics men's team, Swedish system event.
